d_name,message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"96cbb0a2-166a-4005-9678-b226365b4e74\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"eca392c1-8edc-43f2-ae42-297267cef484\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-12T01:10:23.761071627Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"24687d5c-273d-4bc1-83ee-12c1adf013c8\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"2168771e-7ecd-449a-b701-75c8983a1f35\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-12T01:10:37.853341872Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-1"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-12T01:10:18Z to 2025-06-12T01:29:18Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 01:10:18+00:00 to 2025-06-12 01:29:18+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "异常数据加载成功，根据 UDID 为 1193b5d8-230 的调用链追踪信息，以下是检测到的异常摘要与分析资讯。\n\n### 异常摘要：\n1. **时段**: 2025-06-12T01:10:18Z 至 2025-06-12T01:29:18Z。\n2. **异常源服务主要分布**:\n   - `checkoutservice`: 异常请求占主导，关联的多个下游服务异常。\n   - `cartservice`: 多次显示异常状态，包括 `Unavailable` 和连接拒绝。\n3. **错误类型**: \n   - `connection refused`: 表明某些下游服务挂起或网络中断。\n   - `Unavailable`: 通信错误导致请求失败。\n\n---\n\n### 错误与延迟分析：\n- 显著异常延迟集中在 `checkoutservice -> payment`, `cartservice -> redis`。\n- 调用链特别高的延迟倍数如下：\n   - `checkoutservice -> cart`: 正常均值 5216ms，但异常均值高达 **81169.9ms**，延迟约 **16倍**。\n   - `checkoutservice -> paymentservice`: 正常均值 12831ms，但异常均值飙升至 **123373ms**，延迟约 **9.6倍**。\n   - `redis -> cartservice`: 正常均值仅为 1361ms，但异常值达到 **29530ms**，延迟 **21.5倍**。\n\n---\n\n### 错误传播路径：\n根据报错路径，可以推测 `cartservice -> redis` 的异常作为调用链上关键路径，且传播至其他上游模块特别是 `checkoutservice`。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的异常指标分析，已识别的异常主要集中在以下几个节点和服务上：\n\n### 异常数据摘要\n- **时间范围**: 2025-06-12 01:10:18 至 2025-06-12 01:29:18\n- **异常指标**:\n\n  1. **Node级别**:\n     - `aiops-k8s-04` 的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 上升了 47.59%\n\n  2. **Service级别**:\n     - `cartservice` 服务在多个指标上出现异常：\n       - `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 的 P99 增加显著\n       - `rrt_max` 值相对于正常中值显著增加\n       - `rrt` 同样有较高的变化幅度\n\n### 异常组件及原因评估\n\n#### 1. 节点 `aiops-k8s-04`\n- **component**: \"aiops-k8s-04\"\n- **reason**: \"node_memory_usage_rate exhaustion causing potential associated pod performance degradation\"\n- **evidence**: `node_memory_usage_rate` 上升了 47.59%\n\n#### 2. CartService\n- **component**: \"cartservice\"\n- **reason**: \"Significant increases in rrt_max and error_ratio indicating service performance issues\"\n- **evidence**: `error_ratio`, `server_error_ratio` 增加显著，`rrt_max` 中值从 5231.5 增加到 77184.0\n\n### 结论\n1. 由于 `aiops-k8s-04` 节点的内存使用率出现了显著上升，这可能是导致与其上的 pods 性能下降的一个关键原因。\n2. `cartservice` 服务表现出多重性能退化现象，与服务逻辑链中的其他组件 (如 Redis、推荐服务等) 可能出现同步异常有密切关系。\n\n根据以上分析，要真正定位故障，需要结合日志检查 `aiops-k8s-04` 上 pods 的具体运行状况和 `cartservice` 的服务日志信息，以查明内存消耗的根源和客户端错误比例的成因。", "log_analysis_findings": "以下是UDID为1193b5d8-230的异常数据分析结果：\n\n### 错误日志分析\n\n#### 日志摘要\n我们分析了时间段为2025-06-12T01:10:18Z到2025-06-12T01:29:18Z的日志数据，相关的错误日志如下：\n- 日志来自于 `frontend` 服务，分别在不同的节点 `aiops-k8s-03` 和 `aiops-k8s-07`。\n- 错误日志的消息为尝试续订单时发生问题，具体错误为 `rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error`，并包含连接被拒绝（`connection refused`）信息。\n\n#### 关键日志片段\n- `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"`\n\n#### 错误关键词提取\n- `connection refused`\n- `transport: Error while dialing`\n- `rpc error: code = Unavailable`\n\n### 分析结论\n1. **错误类型**: Connection Issue\n   - 提取的关键词明确指出有连接被拒绝的情况。\n   \n2. **嫌疑服务与根因假设**\n   - Frontend 服务在调用一个特定的 IP 地址（10.233.46.196）时出现连接拒绝，表明可能的配置错误或目标服务的网络配置问题。\n   - 该特定 IP 通常是一个服务的内部 Cluster IP，日志以及错误模式表明可能存在端口配置错误。\n\n### 验证根因假设\n- 假设为 `Port Misconfiguration`，被填充的细节为目标服务配置错误的连接端口。\n\n### JSON 格式化输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"port\", \"connection refused\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"目标服务 (配置错误端口的那个服务)\",\n      \"reason\": \"目标服务 连接建立失败: transport: Error while dialing, connection refused\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据以上数据和分析，我们的分析支持当前根因假设，即与端口配置错误有关的连接问题。", "current_hypothesis": "CartService 和 Frontend 服务出现 Port Misconfiguration 导致连接拒绝和性能退化"}
